 {"id": "cst-s0104t.nrf-6_p127", "referent": "epithet", "claim_bearing": false, "facet": null, "claim": null, "note": "Nāgopamasutta-vacana — referring to the Nāga-simile sutta said of the Buddha; epithet (anumānāgama in same row is nonlexical but nāgopama is the codeable nāga)"},
