 {"id": "cst-s0105t.nrf-3_p002", "referent": "epithet", "claim_bearing": false, "facet": null, "claim": null, "note": "esa nāga…pe… viya — Jīvaka/teacher likened to a nāga for utter silence; honorific simile of a person (could pun elephant, but applied to a human)"},
